WEBVTT Offset: 5.467;

03:15.616 --> 03:19.754
As the blue sky disappeared, you perservered

03:19.754 --> 03:23.179
No matter how you felt,

03:23.179 --> 03:26.588
You said "forward's the only path."

03:26.588 --> 03:28.610
That flaming soul I hear,

03:28.610 --> 03:30.970
Let your heart burn free

03:30.970 --> 03:33.648
With passion, you will gleam

03:33.648 --> 03:36.981
Until the sky turns black...

03:37.315 --> 03:42.888
Keep it up!

04:17.949 --> 04:20.388
Just a little more!